LAWRENCEWHITESIDE.COM

This is the application running at Lawrencewhiteside.com
It consists of the javascript, ruby, haml and scss used to create a simple portfolio app.
It is released free and open, same license (non-license as JQuery Tools.)

To be completed with the following as examples of my experience and knowledge.
- RSpec coverage for the server-side.
- Funcunit test coverage for the client-side.
- Comments everywhere to better understand my thought process.

Technologies used include.

Rails 3.2.2
Ruby 1.9.2
Javascript MVC 3.2
HAML/SASS
RSpec 2
Funcunit

Ay questions or comments.  Please email me at law@cinemasetfree.com
Thanks for checking it out.